Lingua-PT-Abbrev

This module handles abbreviations for the Portuguese language. It
includes a default dictionary, and handles a user custom dictionary.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



